{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_01","textHome":"我的名字叫惠萌花，在荣综合学园上学。我的@朋友们都很温柔，我最喜欢她们了。爸爸和@妈妈我也很喜欢。还有，甜甜的点心还有可@爱的小猫之类的……我有特别多喜欢的东西@！啊，我不是在要求你为我做什么哦……！@让你多费心思真是不好意思。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":200}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_17","textHome":"教朋友们学习真的很开心……！所以，我从来@没想过会麻烦什么的。进入大学之后，真想@试试兼职家庭教师啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_18","textHome":"朋友们真的教会了我很多东西……！因为我真@的很不谙世事……不过，大家都说“萌花保@持这个样子就可以了”……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_19","textHome":"对了……！只要能拿这份力量……嘿！地砍过@去的话……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_20","textHome":"啊，感觉……头脑清醒了一点……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_21","textHome":"我直到最近，都一直以为世界上只有漂亮而可@爱的东西……但是，现在……我已经不再是@看不清楚现实的小孩子了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_22","textHome":"我身边的人们都很温柔，也会拉着我远离危险@肮脏的东西。但是，我也不能一直这样下去@……！我也要获得更多更多的力量，最后变@得能够独当一面，然后和大家一起战斗……@！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_23","textHome":"在我不知道的地方，也一定有人在哭泣。至今@为止我一直悠闲地生活过来了，但与之相应@，这次轮到我来帮助大家了……！是这样吧@？那个时候我被搭救下来，就是这么回事吧@……我成功发生改变了吗……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303400}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_24","textHome":"哇——！今天也和你见面了呢！一起来，……@聊聊天吧！对了……！我正好发现了一家不@错的咖啡厅。我们就在那里说话吧，好吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_25","textHome":"呼啊……早上好……好困啊……今天干脆就…@…别起床了……不行！今天我得去买滑溜溜@的布丁才行！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_26","textHome":"到了我翘首以盼的中午了！……诶？便当……@你忘带了吗……？……那、那要不要我稍微@分一点给你？来，张嘴——……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_02","textHome":"初次见面，我是惠萌花。为了不拉大家的后退@……我会尽全力加油的……我不会做多余的@事情的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_27","textHome":"今天马上也要结束了呢……今天，我笨手笨脚@的次数只有4次……嗯。做得不错……，做@得不错……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303400}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_28","textHome":"睡不着……因为我看了个恐怖片……明明早知@道会变成这样的……今天我连厕所也不敢去@了……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303400}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_29","textHome":"这个钥匙扣？是一个叫“阴沉每一天”的动画@里的角色……它很可爱，而且看起来很散漫@，好像完全没在思考，很让人安心呢……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_30","textHome":"这个气息……有魔女在前面等着……！魔女…@…很可怕……为什么要这样……吓唬我呢…@…？我不喜欢这种坏心眼的做法啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_31","textHome":"那边的魔法少女们是假的吗……？的确……里@面也有长得和我一模一样的人呢……总感觉@，那是至今为止最弱的对手……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_32","textHome":"哈哇……有好多魔法少女呀。必须去跟每个人@都打一遍招呼才行……虽然感觉打完招呼太@阳就都要落山了，但打招呼是很重要的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.6,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_33","textHome":"前段时间，我收拾房间的时候……发现了一篇@自己小时候写的，叫做“未来的梦想”的作@文……上面写着，我将来想变成一颗草莓…@…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_34","textHome":"虽然大家会送我很多点心……但是，有时候我@也会吃不完……这种时候，我的朋友就会给@我做一个写着“请勿投喂”的牌子。……投@喂？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_35","textHome":"我看见药店里有卖装在喷雾罐里的奶油冻，就@想买点回去，但是有人告诉我那是用来涂在@头发上的，阻止了我……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_36","textHome":"呜～！好不甘心！……丘比……明明很可爱吧@……？但是大家对它的评价似乎都很糟糕…@…它应该得到更高的评价！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_03","textHome":"虽然可能有点危险……但我也有重要的使命！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_37","textHome":"班上的同学都很温柔、很有精神，在学校的每@一天都很开心！之前我冷到颤抖不止的时候@，就会有人抱紧我让我取暖……！诶嘿嘿…@…！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":1,"id":303400}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_38","textHome":"美雨……既知识渊博、头脑灵光，又强大、温@柔、帅气，和我完全不一样啊……下辈子我@想当美雨……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_39","textHome":"雏乃……经常会喝我喝不下去的好像很苦的咖@啡……真有大人样呢……！但是，我却被她@说着“真讨人厌！？”骂了一顿……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_40","textHome":"美术社的御园同学……看起来非常寂寞……如@果我再多一点勇气和力量……那个人就……@不会消失了吧……我真不争气啊……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.9,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":303400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":0}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_41","textHome":"我……经常被朋友骂，说我太没有防备了……@今天我就差点在教室里换了衣服，但是当时@还有男生在场……我一定吓了他们一跳吧…@…"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":303400,"motion":200}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_42","textHome":"我、我要把你们打飞……！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":303400,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3034_00_43","textHome":"没、没事吧……！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeC